content: --कल (निष्कंल) {%<ab>a.</ab>%} {1} without parts, undivided, whole. {2} waned, decayed, diminished. {3} impotent, barren. {4} maimed. (--लः {1} a receptacle. {2} the pudendum muliebre. {3} <ab>N.</ab> of Brahmā. (ला, --ली) an elderly woman, one who is past child-bearing, or one in whom menstruation has ceased.
